00:12:10,784 --> 00:12:12,883
Ayolah, Ayumi!

219
00:12:12,884 --> 00:12:14,184
Ayumi!

220
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:35,139
Apa? Conan?

221
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:36,239
Ayumi!

222
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,039
Apa kau baik-baik saja?

223
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:40,239
Oh, semuanya.

224
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,439
Apa kau merasa kesakitan?

225
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:45,039
Kau sepertinya tidak terluka, tapi...

226
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:47,539
Aku baik-baik saja. Tidak ada rasa sakit sama sekali.

227
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:49,339
Bisa bicara sebentar?

228
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:50,939
Ya.

229
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:53,239
Apa yang terjadi?

230
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,539
Itu...

231
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:57,539
Kau melihat seorang gadis?

232
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:58,639
Ya.

233
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:01,839
Dia berusia sekitar 10 tahun, rambut bob,

234
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,739
